reviews.body:
The changes fixed the bugs from the issue! I noticed there are some other cases of `Bool` conversion that should work. For example,

```sql
SELECT CAST(1, 'Nullable(Bool)') IN (toNullable(10));
0
SELECT CAST(1, 'Nullable(Bool)') IN (toNullable(255));
0
SELECT CAST(1, 'Nullable(Bool)') IN (toNullable(256));
1
SELECT CAST(1, 'Nullable(Bool)') IN (toNullable(1000));
1
```
I think it might be best if we fix them with this PR. 

Additionally, the PR has additionally fixed the following kind of queries:

```sql
SELECT toLowCardinality(CAST(1, 'Bool')) IN (10);
SELECT toLowCardinality(CAST(1, 'Bool')) IN (255);
```

Let's add these to tests as well.
